snippet: The Air Force said Thursday that it had determined why two more pilots recently experienced oxygen problems in the F-22 Raptor, the stealthy fighter jet.
abstract: Air Force identifies malfunctions in life support systems that have caused two more pilots to experience oxygen problems while operating the F-22 Raptor.
lead_paragraph: The Air Force said Thursday that it had determined why two more pilots recently experienced oxygen problems in the F-22 Raptor, the stealthy fighter jet.
